{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2014}} {{Infobox musical artist | image = | name = Aman Hayer | birth_name = Amandip Singh Hayer | alias = "The Groundshaker" or "The Entourage" | birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=y|1979|11|05}} Lidhran, Jalandhar, Punjab, India | origin = | genre = [[Bhangra (music)|Bhangra]] | associated_acts = | occupation = Record producer, music director, singer, songwriter, musician, composer | years_active = 1998–present | label = Elite Music Worldwide | website = www.amanhayer.com [http://www.amanhayer.com] }} '''Amandip Singh Hayer''' ([[Punjabi language|Punjabi]]: ਅਮਨਦੀਪ ਸਿੰਘ ਹਾਈਯਰ, born 5 November 1979) better known as '''Aman Hayer''', is a UK-based [[Bhangra (music)|Bhangra]] Punjabi music director and singer.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://simplybhangra.com/interviews/artist-interviews/3798-exclusive-interview-with-aman-hayer | title=Exclusive Interview with Aman Hayer | publisher=Simply Bhangra | accessdate=1 September 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.punjabiportal.com/forum/aman-hayer-songs-music-albums-videos-t6853.html | title=Aman Hayer – Biography & More | publisher=Punjabi Portal | accessdate=1 September 2012 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120824104304/http://www.punjabiportal.com/forum/aman-hayer-songs-music-albums-videos-t6853.html | archive-date=24 August 2012 | url-status=dead | df=dmy-all }}</ref>
Aman Hayer is a Punjabi Bhangra artist. He is known for his albums Reminisce & Groundshaker I & II.
Born in 1978 in Leamington Spa, he started his music career in the early 2000s, working on a number of artists albums including Amar Arshi's 'Dark Angel', Amar Group's 'Desi In Ya Face', and Saabs' 'First Contact'.
==Career== Hayer has produced seven albums of his own, ''Deja Vu'' (2002), ''Reminisce'' (2003), ''Groundshaker'' (2005), ''Groundshaker II'' (2008), ''Nachdi De EP'' (2009), ''Ajj Nachna EP'' (2011) and ''The Entourage'' (2011), and has launched careers of [[Kulwinder Dhillon]], [[Angrej Ali]] and Nirmal Sidhu and [[Benny Dhaliwal]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.amanhayer.com/ | title=Past, Present, and Future | publisher=Aman Hayer | accessdate=1 September 2012}}</ref> Aman Hayer now has his own DJ Roadshow called 'The Entourage Roadshow' where he takes many singers from his camp to perform such as Angrej Ali, Sherry Maan, Mangi Mahal, Benny Dhaliwal, Sarbjit Cheema, K S Makhan, Geeta Zaildar, Dev Dhillon, Gippy Grewal & Rasshee Rraga. Currently Aman Hayer Plays the Dhol, Dholki, Tabla, Keyboard and Harmonium.
