==Current work== Williams currently teaches at The University of Melbourne.{{citation needed|date=May 2019}}
He still releases music on his Bandcamp page. The most recent releases were ''The Sidewinder Project'', which was a collection of collaborations in 1997/1998 and ''Cosmic Love EP''.{{citation needed|date=July 2020}}
