==Jug Band==
In addition to his work in entertainment music scoring, Jared is also the front man of the [[Rivertown Skifflers]], a northern California based [[jug band]]. <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rivertownskifflers.com/about|title=About}}</ref>
